Class Tile

java.lang.Object
Tile
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlueTile, GreenTile, RedTile
public abstract class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents the tiles of the game. The tiles: Blue tile, Red tile, Green tile.
